<div class="content-centered">
  <h1>Growth API</h1>
  <p class="mb-3">Analytics platform for subscription-based applications. Track user behavior, manage subscriptions, and gain insights with our robust API.</p>
  <div class="d-flex justify-center gap-2 mb-3">
    <%= link_to "View API Docs", "https://documenter.getpostman.com/view/29345048/2sB34oBcx7", class: "btn btn-secondary", target: "_blank" %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3>🔐 JWT Authentication</h3>
      </div>
      <p>Secure user registration and login with stateless JWT tokens. Supports both API and web authentication flows.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3>💳 Subscription Management</h3>
      </div>
      <p>Handle free and premium tiers with upgrade/downgrade capabilities. Track subscription events and billing changes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3>📊 Event Tracking</h3>
      </div>
      <p>Log user activities, authentication events, and system interactions. MongoDB storage for high-volume event data.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3>⚡ Rate Limiting</h3>
      </div>
      <p>Built-in API rate limiting per IP address. Redis-backed for fast, distributed rate limit enforcement.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3>🛡️ Admin Dashboard</h3>
      </div>
      <p>Role-based access control with admin analytics. Monitor user activity, subscription metrics, and system health.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3>🚀 Production Ready</h3>
      </div>
      <p>Docker deployment, background job processing with Sidekiq, comprehensive error handling, and CI/CD pipeline.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="content text-center mt-3">
    <h2>API Endpoints</h2>
    <div style="text-align: left; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p><strong>POST</strong> <code>/v1/login</code> - Authenticate and get JWT</p>
      <p><strong>GET</strong> <code>/v1/profile</code> - Get user details</p>
      <p><strong>POST</strong> <code>/v1/subscribe</code> - Upgrade to premium</p>
      <p><strong>POST</strong> <code>/v1/event</code> - Log user activity</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-3">
      <p>Ready to integrate? Check the <%= link_to "API documentation", "https://documenter.getpostman.com/view/29345048/2sB34oBcx7", target: "_blank" %> for detailed examples.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
